name: 摩美々
text: おはよーございまぁす
trans: Goood morning...

name: 摩美々
text:
（んー？　……なんだか、
事務所が服だらけになってるー……）
trans:
(Hmm? Somehow, the office is piled up with clothes
everywhere...)

name: 摩美々
text: （あ、あそこにいるの……三峰かな）
trans: (Ah... Maybe Mitsumine had something to do with it.)

name: 結華
text:
お、まみみんだ
おはよー
trans: Ah! It's Mamimin! Good morning～

name: 摩美々
text: おはよー三峰
trans: Morning, Mitsumine.

name: 摩美々
text:
これ全部三峰の服―？
……足の踏み場がないねー
trans:
Are all these clothes yooours?
...I can barely find a place to stand.

name: 結華
text: ごめんごめん、散らかしすぎちゃった
trans: Yeaaah, sorry about all the mess.

name: 摩美々
text:
三峰ほどじゃないけど、私もけっこー持って来ちゃったぁ
これねー
trans:
I brought some of mine too, Mitsumine.
But not as much as you did. Here you gooo.

name: 結華
text:
おー、可愛い服がいっぱい！
じゃあじゃあ始めちゃう？
trans:
Ohhh, so many cute clothes!
Well then, shall we get started?

name: 摩美々
text:
うん、いいよー
私も三峰に着せる服、考えるからぁ
trans:
Suuure, that's fine.
I'll come up with something for you to wear.

name: 結華
text: いやー、この攻撃的な服！　実にまみみんらしいなぁ
trans:
Oh boooy, these clothes are so wild!
Very on brand for Mamimin.

name: 摩美々
text:
原色と一面に広がる幾何学模様……
こういうの三峰好きそうー
trans:
Primary colors patterned with geometric shapes...
So this is what Mitsumine likes...

name: 結華
text:
へぇー……こんな服もあるんだ
どこに売ってるんだろ？
trans:
Whoa, there are clothes like this?
I wonder where they're selling these?

name: 摩美々
text:
あ、かわいいかもー
こーゆータイプのは知らなかったな
trans:
Huh, this one's real cute.
I never seen anything like this before.

name: 結華
text:
うん？　これもまたすごいねぇ
ダメージ加工レベル100みたいになってる
trans:
Hmm? This one's pretty crazy-looking, huh?
It's as if it took damage from a Lv. 100.

name: 結華
text: これもすごくまみみんって感じ
trans: This one here's also very much like you, Mamimin!

name: 結華
text:
あー待って、こっちとこれ合わせたらすごく……
おおお、いいんじゃないです！？
trans:
Ah hold up, if you combo these together, then...
Ohhhh?! Doesn't this look amazing?!

name: 摩美々
text:
これもいい感じー
さっきのと合わせるといいかもー
trans:
This one's good toooo.
It might be nice to match it with the one from earlier.

name: 摩美々
text:
三峰の服はカラフルだねー
だけど、ここにキレを足したいかもー
trans:
Mitsumine's clothes are colorful, huh?
But, I think I want to layer these pieces.

name: 結華
text:
ねぇねぇまみみん！　
ちょっとまみみんの服着てみてもいい？
trans:
Hey hey, Mamimin!
Can I try putting on some of your clothes for a bit?

name: 摩美々
text: 別にいいけど、どうしたのー？
trans: I don't miiind. But why?

name: 結華
text:
どうしても気になるのがあってさ！
ありがと、着させてもらうね！
trans:
I just can't resist trying them out!
Thanks for letting me wear them!

name: 結華
text: 見て見て、これどうかな？
trans: Check it out! How does it look?

name: 摩美々
text:
いい感じで、似合ってるよー
可愛いと思うー
trans:
Looking gooood.
I think it looks cute on you.

name: 結華
text: やーった！　まみみんのお墨付き！
trans: Woohoo! I got Mamimin's seal of approval!

name: 摩美々
text:
あれー？　
でもー、お互いにコーディネートするんじゃないのー？
trans:
Huuuh? But weren't we supposed to
coordinate for each other?

name: 摩美々
text: 三峰、自分で服着ちゃってるしー
trans: Mitsumine... You went ahead and dressed yourself up.

name: 結華
text:
いやぁごめん、我慢できなくってさぁ
三峰の素敵な服アンテナが反応しちゃったんだよ！
trans:
My bad, I couldn't resist!
Mitsumine's Drip Radar was swarmed with pings!

name: 摩美々
text: ……それじゃあ、しょーがないかもー？
trans: Mmm... Then I guess, there's no problem?

name: 結華
text: ついでにまみみんも何か着てみる？
trans:
Anyways, Mamimin...
Don't you want to try something on?

name: 摩美々
text:
そうだねー三峰も着てるし、
私も着てみよーかなぁ
trans:
Well since you're wearing mine,
then maaaybe I should wear yours.

name: 結華
text:
おっけおっけ！
三峰のおすすめはね……んーっと……
trans:
Okay okay!
Mitsumine recommends... Hmm...

name: 結華
text:
あ、ほらっ、これとか、これもおすすめ！
あとこっちも気に入ってるんだ～！
trans:
Ah, maybe this one! And this one too!
I'm loving this piece over here too～!

name: 摩美々
text:
へー、面白い服だねー
あ、これに私の服合わせたら、もっと面白くなりそー
trans:
Huh, that's an interesting outfit... Oh, it'll even be
mooore interesting if I pair with my clothes too, huh?

name: 結華
text:
わかる！　楽しそう！
どっちの服も混ぜて自由にコーデしちゃおうよ！
trans:
Exactly! This is gonna be fun!
We can mash our styles together!

name: 結華
text: やっぱりまみみん超かわいい！
trans: Mamimin's clothes are super cute after all!

name: 結華
text:
ポップ路線も行けちゃうんだねぇ
フリフリだしキラキラだし、お人形さんみたいになってるよ
trans:
I see you can pull off a more pop style too!
You look all fluffy and sparkly, just like a doll!

name: 摩美々
text:
んー、いつもだったら選ばないケド
この服は悪くないかもー
trans:
Hmm, while I don't normally wear something like this,
maybe this outfit isn't half-bad at all.

name: 結華
text: ほんと？　お気に召したなら何より
trans: Really? I'm glad you like it!

name: 摩美々
text:
いい感じだと思うー
この服、気に入っちゃったかもー
trans:
This outfit reaaally does look good.
I think I might even wear it myself.

name: 結華
text: そう言ってくれるともっとやる気になっちゃうよー！
trans: Saying that pumps me up even more!

name: 結華
text:
まだこれも着てほしいし、あのプリントが派手めな服も
着てほしいんだよね！　迷っちゃうな～
trans:
You still gotta wear this one!
Or maybe the one with the flashy print too!
I don't know where to start～

name: 摩美々
text: あ、それなら私もー、三峰に着て欲しい服があるかもー
trans:
Ah, I got something.
I might have some clothes for you, Mitsumine.

name: 結華
text:
どれどれ見せてー？
まみみんにも選んでほし……
trans:
Oh, which ones will you show me?
I want to pick out clothes for you too, Mamimin...

name: 摩美々
text: 三峰どうしたのー？
trans: Is something wrooong, Mitsumine?

name: 結華
text: あーっ、もうレッスンが始まる時間じゃーん！
trans: Ahhh! Our lesson's about to start!

name: 摩美々
text:
あ、そーいえばぁ……
いいところだったんだケドー
trans:
Oh, you're right...
Must've lost track of time.

name: 結華
text:
今日のところはここまでだねぇ
レッスンのこと忘れてたよ……
trans:
I guess that's it for today...
Can't believe we forgot about the lesson...

name: 摩美々
text:
まーしょーがないねー
けっこー楽しかったからぁ、いいってことでー
trans:
Weeell, it isn't all baaad.
We had fun, so it's fiiine.

name: 結華
text:
そうだね！
この感じで本番のお仕事もがんばろうね！
trans:
You're right!
Let's be sure to use this energy for work!

name: 摩美々
text: あ、そーいえばこれ仕事のための衣装合わせだったんだぁ
trans:
Ah, come to think of it...
This was all for that one job, huh?

name: 結華
text: 忘れてたのまみみん！？
trans: Did you really forget about it, Mamimin?!

name: 摩美々
text: ふふー、どーかなぁ
trans: Fufu, did I?

name: 結華
text:
って、それより片付けしなきゃだよ！
レッスンに間に合わないー！
trans:
Hey, we need to clean this up faster!
We'll be late for our lesson!

name: 摩美々
text: 手分けしてさっさと終わらせよー
trans: We'll get it over with if we split the tasks.

name: 摩美々
text:
……ねーねー三峰、よかったらさぁ
また、三峰の服みせてよー
trans:
...Hey Mitsumine. If you don't mind, you should
show me more of your clothes next time.

name: 結華
text:
もちろん！
まみみんだったら大歓迎だよ
trans:
I don't mind!
You're welcome anytime, Mamimin!

name: 摩美々
text:
ふふー、よかったぁ
お願いねー
trans:
Fufu, good to hear.
Please and thank you.
